    <item>
      <title>瑞典房地产、矿业股引领欧洲美联储后反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/swedish-real-estate-wind-stocks-top-post-fed-rally-in-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美联储转向扭转大幅加息的方向后，瑞典房地产股和矿业公司等欧洲股市遭受重创的板块纷纷飙升。英国央行维持利率不变后，市场保持上涨，投资者现在正在为欧洲央行的决定做准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/swedish-real-estate-wind-stocks-top-post-fed-rally-in-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 08:15:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>银行家躲避欧洲迄今为止最严厉的 ESG 法的全面影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/banks-win-reprieve-from-landmark-eu-law-on-due-diligence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着欧盟达成妥协以帮助该法案顺利通过，金融业将免受欧盟迄今为止最重要的 ESG 立法的全部影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/banks-win-reprieve-from-landmark-eu-law-on-due-diligence</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 07:02:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储后股市与债券一起上涨；欧元上涨：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在通胀压力正在缓解的乐观情绪中，美联储的鸽派信号释放了整个市场的看涨脉搏，华尔街准备延续涨势。在欧洲央行如预期维持利率不变后，欧元维持早前涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 23:40:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
